title: What’s On Your Throne | Joel Osteen

description:
God wants to reign in your life in a new way. The time is coming for you to experience His favor like never before.

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
